  "title": "TECHNICAL SALES ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Technical Sales Engineer is responsible for achieving sales targets by managing client quotations, contracts, and documentation while driving business development and ensuring compliance with health, safety, and environmental standards.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver sales and rental quotes to clients accurately and promptly to support contract finalization</li><li>Organize and update contracts and quotations according to client RFQs to maintain accurate records on system</li><li>Ensure all necessary project documentation is provided to clients before project commencement to facilitate smooth operations</li><li>Acquire and apply foundational knowledge of the use, service, and maintenance of the company’s rental equipment to support client interactions</li><li>Proactively identify and pursue new business opportunities with existing and potential customers to drive revenue growth</li><li>Arrange and conduct multiple client meetings annually, preparing detailed reports for the Commercial Manager to inform strategic decisions</li><li>Collaborate with suppliers to coordinate cross hires and purchases, ensuring contract compliance and timely delivery</li><li>Actively participate in and implement the company’s Health, Safety, and Environmental (HSE) policies in daily work to maintain a safe workplace</li></ul>",
